you don't even have to speak english...you're native language would be ok...but I think since you'd be applying from the US you'd be expected to speak english...<br>
it's arranged through the japanese ministry of foreign affairs...<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.mofa.go.jp/j_info/visit/jet/index.html">www.mofa.go.jp/j_info/visit/jet/index.html</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
